<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, June 12 (Xinhua) -- A prosecutor Thursday urged
jurors to have the courage to put the Oklahoma City bomber Timothy
McVeigh to death, while McVeigh's attorneys portrayed him as a
misguided patriot.
