<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, June 13 (Xinhua) -- The Chief Executive's Office of
the Hong Kong Special Administrative Region (HKSAR) today
published the Oaths and Declarations (Amendment) Bill 1997.
</P>
<P>
