<HEADLINE> 20 People Die When Building Collapses in Nigeria </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LAGOS, June 13 (Xinhua) -- No fewer than 20 persons were killed in
Enugu State, southeast Nigeria, on Thursday, when a three-storey
building under construction collapsed.
</P>
<P>
