<HEADLINE> S. African Sugar Giant Enters into Swaziland's </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JOHANNESBURG, June 13 (Xinhua) -- Illovo Sugar, South Africa's
major sugar producer, has announced that it will be listed on the
Swaziland Stock Exchange.
</P>
<P>
