Car Works also runs a special technical school to train more
professionals.
</P>
<P>
When the US company started to tap the Chinese market last
year, it launched two production lines in areas such as coastal
Shanghai, Nanjing, and Dulaying of Guizhou, respectively. Today
there are already 14 such production lines in Dulaying, making it
the company's biggest production base of micro-electrical
appliances in China.
</P>
<P>
"Both experts and our clients are satisfied with quality of
products from the joint venture in Dulaying, and personally I'm
definitely sure that more and more foreign businesses will come to
discover here an ideal place to make investment," said Eric
Gravell. 
