<HEADLINE> Berasategui to Take on Kuerten </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ROME, June 12 (Xinhua) -- Top seed Alberto Berasategui will
meet French Open champion Gustavo Kuerten in the quarter finals
after beating fellow Thursday at the Bologna international men's
clay-court tournament.
</P>
<P>
Berasategui, ranked 14 in the world, scored a 6-2, 6-3 win over
fellow Spaniard Albert Portas, entering the quarter finals.
</P>
<P>
