<HEADLINE> Part of Guangzhou's Subway to Open Soon </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
GUANGZHOU, June 13 (Xinhua) -- The first section of the 18.48
km-long Guangzhou No. One Metro, the first subway of its kind in
the capital city of South China's Guangdong Province, is to become
operational on June 28.
</P>
<P>
The Guangzhou Metro Operation Company, owner of the subway, has
sent over 700 of its staff for training in subway companies in
Hong Kong and Shanghai.
</P>
<P>
